#: prefs.js:1116
msgid "💡 How to find the correct App ID?"
msgstr "💡 Bagaimana cara menemukan App ID yang benar?"

#: prefs.js:1117
msgid "Click here for a quick guide and examples"
msgstr "Klik di sini untuk panduan singkat dan contoh"

#: prefs.js:1121
msgid ""
"To allow the extension to open/close your player, you need to provide its "
"exact window name (App ID).\n"
"\n"
"<b>Common Examples:</b>\n"
"• Spotify (Flatpak): <b>com.spotify.Client</b>\n"
"• VLC: <b>vlc</b>\n"
"• YouTube Music (Web App): <b>youtube-music</b>\n"
"• High Tide: <b>io.github.nokse22.high-tide</b>\n"
"• Browsers: <b>chromium</b>, <b>firefox</b>, <b>brave-browser</b>\n"
"\n"
"<b>How to find it manually:</b>\n"
"1. Press <b>Alt + F2</b>, type <b>lg</b>, and press Enter.\n"
"2. Click on the <b>Windows</b> tab in the top right corner.\n"
"3. Find your music player in the list.\n"
"4. Look at the <b>wmclass:</b> or <b>app:</b> field. That is your App ID! "
"<i>(Remove the .desktop part)</i>\n"
"5. Press Esc to close the debugger."
msgstr ""
"Agar ekstensi dapat membuka/menutup pemutar Anda, Anda perlu memberikan nama "
"jendelanya yang tepat (App ID).\n"
"\n"
"<b>Contoh Umum:</b>\n"
"-  Spotify (Flatpak): <b>com.spotify.Client</b>\n"
"-  VLC: <b>vlc</b>\n"
"-  YouTube Music (Aplikasi Web): <b>youtube-music</b>\n"
"-  High Tide: <b>io.github.nokse22.high-tide</b>\n"
"-  Browser: <b>chromium</b>, <b>firefox</b>, <b>brave-browser</b>\n"
"\n"
"<b>Cara menemukannya secara manual:</b>\n"
"1. Tekan <b>Alt + F2</b>, ketik <b>lg</b>, lalu tekan Enter.\n"
"2. Klik tab <b>Windows</b> di kanan atas.\n"
"3. Temukan pemutar musik Anda dalam daftar.\n"
"4. Lihat kolom <b>wmclass:</b> atau <b>app:</b>. Itulah App ID Anda! <i>"
"(Hapus bagian .desktop)</i>\n"
"5. Tekan Esc untuk menutup debugger."

